<doc id="496986" wikidata="Q7968626" url="?curid=496986" title="War in the Kitchen">
<text>War in the Kitchen () is a Romanian film drama by Marius Theodor Barna. The film was produced in 2001 by Ager Film in collaboration with Televiziunea Română (TVR). It stars Gheorghe Dinică as the main actor.

